<Link id="l00385" /><CodeLine lineNumber="385"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// then added back newly found call sites.  One thing that can happen is</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00390" /><CodeLine lineNumber="390"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// just look at whether the number of indirect calls is reduced and the</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00391" /><CodeLine lineNumber="391"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// number of direct calls is increased.  There are tons of ways to fool this</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00392" /><CodeLine lineNumber="392"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// (e.g. DCE&#39;ing an indirect call and duplicating an unrelated block with a</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00516" /><CodeLine lineNumber="516"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// functions in this SCC.  However, we support iterative compilation in the</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00517" /><CodeLine lineNumber="517"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// case where a function pass devirtualizes a call to a function.  For</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00518" /><CodeLine lineNumber="518"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// example, it is very common for a function pass (often GVN or instcombine)</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00519" /><CodeLine lineNumber="519"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// to eliminate the addressing that feeds into a call.  With that improved</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00520" /><CodeLine lineNumber="520"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// information, we would like the call to be an inline candidate, infer</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00521" /><CodeLine lineNumber="521"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// mod-ref information etc.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00522" /><CodeLine lineNumber="522"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">//</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00523" /><CodeLine lineNumber="523"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Because of this, we allow iteration up to a specified iteration count.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00524" /><CodeLine lineNumber="524"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// This only happens in the case of a devirtualized call, so we only burn</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00525" /><CodeLine lineNumber="525"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// compile time in the case that we&#39;re making progress.  We also have a hard</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00526" /><CodeLine lineNumber="526"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// iteration count limit in case there is crazy code.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00527" /><CodeLine lineNumber="527"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">unsigned</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> Iteration = 0;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00528" /><CodeLine lineNumber="528"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">bool</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> DevirtualizedCall = </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">false</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00529" /><CodeLine lineNumber="529"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">do</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00531" /><CodeLine lineNumber="531"><Highlight kind="normal">                 &lt;&lt; </Highlight><Highlight kind="stringliteral">&quot;  SCCPASSMGR: Re-visiting SCC, iteration #&quot;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &lt;&lt; Iteration</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00532" /><CodeLine lineNumber="532"><Highlight kind="normal">                 &lt;&lt; </Highlight><Highlight kind="charliteral">&#39;\\n&#39;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal">);</Highlight></CodeLine>
